dream_contents: I was being chased and flying in space in the dark when suddenly I landed on the moon. I then was engulfed in the dark as the sun went dim. I was really scared.
I was climbing a high mountain when I was traveling. At the top there were hikers who invited me to a big meal as a celebration. The food was very yummy.
I started my dream looking at a mirror. I was wearing a strange mask with feathers. I turned on the shower and no water came out. I woke up very confused.
I don't remember much, but I remember driving on a road for a long time. The road came to an end and I got out of the car. Below me was a massive river with lots of water flowing. It was magnificent.
I ate a huge meal at a wedding celebration. The bride and groom very very happy and it was a fun dream.
I was being chased by a giant snake in the dark.
I skeleton and ghost were throwing a celebration with lots of food. They were very nice!
I was driving on a long road and pulled off the highway to eat a big meal.
I was at a large wedding.
I was being chased by a ghost in a scooby doo episode with Mystery Inc.
I died in my dream. It was very frightening.
I was at a family wedding and we ate a huge cake.
I was moving houses and drove on a road with my stuff for twelve hours and moved to California.
There was a large earthquake and storm at the same time.
I was in a fire with lots of flames. Then my teeth fell out.
My boss yelled at me for being late to work. The road was backed up on my drive. I got fired.
I was falling after climbing up a mountain. I fell into a stream of water which broke my fall.
I was falling after flying in space.
Someone chased me with a gun and I missed a bus on the road. And there were ghosts on the bus.
